videos.description: Luka Doncic displays some fancy dribbling around defenders, then hits a step-back 3-pointer on Tobias Harris and gives a smile as he runs back on defense.

videos.headline: Doncic smiles after draining step-back 3 on Harris

videos.description: Ben Simmons splits two Mavericks defenders as he jets to the basket to throw down a sweet dunk for the 76ers.
